    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>On page 153 the helper paths/prefixes shown in comments are somehow mixed up. This is a major problem for anyone learning for ZFCE.</p>

<p>When added like:
$view-&gt;addHelperPath('path/to/some..', 'My_View_Helper');
$view-&gt;addHelperPath('other/path...', 'Your_View_Helper');</p>

<p>I think it should be:
1) Your_View_Helper / other/path...
2) My_View_Helper / path/to/some...
3) Zend_View_Helper / Zend/View/...</p>

